comment:
* Captures the user's sleep length and its stages. Each record represents a time interval for a * full sleep session. * *

All {@link Stage} time intervals should fall within the sleep session interval. Time intervals * for stages don't need to be continuous but shouldn't overlap.

variables.name: SLEEP_DURATION_TOTAL
variables.comment:
* Metric identifier to retrieve total sleep session duration using aggregate APIs in {@link
     * android.health.connect.HealthConnectManager}. Calculated in milliseconds.

methods.name: public CharSequence getNotes()
methods.comment: Returns notes for the sleep session. Returns null if no notes was specified.

methods.name: public CharSequence getTitle()
methods.comment: Returns title of the sleep session. Returns null if no notes was specified.

methods.name: public List<Stage> getStages()
methods.comment: Returns stages of the sleep session.
